// Include in job responses
interface JobResponse {
  jobId: string;
  serverInstanceId: string;  // Helps clients detect restart
  // ...
}
```

### Shutdown Safety

```typescript
class JobManager {
  private activeJobs = new Set<Promise<unknown>>();

  async shutdown(): Promise<void> {
    await Promise.all([...this.activeJobs]);
  }
}
```

### Error Containment

Jobs wrapped with .catch().finally() - failures don't crash server.

### Session Lifetime

Jobs per-session (in-memory). Lost on restart, NOT_FOUND after.

### Retention Policy

- 1 hour for completed
- Max 100 retained
- Running never expire

