### Critical Fix #1: CSRF Protection

Current `routeApi()` has Origin check but is unused. Live server has no CSRF protection.

**Solution:**
1. Create `src/serve/security.ts` with shared CSRF guard
2. Enforce Origin header = `localhost` or `127.0.0.1` on all non-GET/HEAD
3. Apply to ALL routes in `server.ts`, not just new write endpoints
