Replace current top-rank bonus with tiered approach matching best practices.

## Current (gno)
```typescript
// Only applies if in top 5 of BOTH bm25 and vector
if (candidate.bm25Rank <= 5 && candidate.vecRank <= 5) {
  candidate.fusionScore += 0.1;
}
```

## New (match competitor)
```typescript
for (const candidate of candidates.values()) {
  let bonus = 0;
  if (candidate.bm25Rank === 1 || candidate.vecRank === 1) {
    bonus = 0.05;  // Ranked #1 in any list
  } else if ((candidate.bm25Rank && candidate.bm25Rank <= 3) ||
             (candidate.vecRank && candidate.vecRank <= 3)) {
    bonus = 0.02;  // Ranked top-3 in any list
  }
  candidate.fusionScore += bonus;
}
```

## Rationale
- Prevents dilution of exact matches by expansion queries
- Rewards documents that rank highly in ANY list, not requiring both

